description: This data, exported from Google Analytics, demonstrates group of interactions that took place on Austintexas.gov pages. A single session can contain multiple screen or page views, events, social interactions, and ecommerce transactions. Pageviews represent a view of a single page. The session duration is the length of time that a visitor remained on Austintexas.gov, and the pages per session show the number of pages they visited during that time.
